hopobject.body: Whereabouts are you from? sinequan capsules Arts Council Wales holds MTW up to its other clients as exemplary in its practice and attitudes, and it has been generous in consequence (its annual grant currently stands at Â£225k). Yet finding private donors to fill the gaps between subsidy and box office is very hard indeed. “We can’t pretend to provide predictable entertainment: we’re an innovation company – something that’s always different and, we hope, exciting,” says Executive Director Carole Strachan. “But people are understandably reluctant to invest in something which has an entirely unknown outcome.”
